These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
7 different games are played: poker, monopoly, snooker, domino, canasta, mah-jongg, backgammon
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing domino is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 6. the american is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
14. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
15. the person playing canasta is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Game          | snooker    | poker    | monopoly | mah-jongg | domino | canasta    | backgammon |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

