.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cabbage, grapefruit, pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, november, may, september, july, october, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the person eating banana##7
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in november##7
 6. the person eating radish is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 7. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating banana##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
10. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
11. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person eating zucchini##6
12. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person eating grapefruit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | zucchini  | cabbage | radish | grapefruit | artichoke     | pomegranate | banana  |
| Birthday   | may | october | november  | march  | july | september      | april |

