 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating lemon##7
10. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person eating pumpkin##6
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
14. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
16. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person eating radish##6
17. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
18. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
