 4. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the cat##7
 7. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
 9. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the goat##1
10. the person driving the car is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the goldfish##2
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
12. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
15. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
16. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
17. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
